OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly fine but cloudy, Light
OL,6,Frain moving in from the west during
OL,7,Fthe afternoon in the north of the
OL,8,Fregion. Winds generally light, though
OL,9,Ffreshening along coasts during the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Warm and humid throughout.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly cloudy, any lingering
OL,13,Frain soon clearing north. A band of
OL,14,Fheavy, perhaps thundery, showers may
OL,15,Fmove north overnight. Remaining rather
OL,16,Fwarm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
