OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAny early heavy, thundery,
OL,6,Fshowers soon clearing northeast to
OL,7,Fleave a dry but mostly cloudy day.
OL,8,FSunshine developing into the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Very warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry and sunny. Chance of thundery
OL,13,Fshowers developing later Thursday and
OL,14,Fcontinuing into early Friday. Widely
OL,15,Fvery warm or hot, including at night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
